Revision history for Parallel-ForkManager-Segmented

0.10.1      2020-10-28

    - Add links to newer alternatives and improve the "SEE ALSO" section.

0.10.0      2020-09-30

    - Use serial_run() from Parallel::ForkManager::Segmented::Base v0.4.0.
        - Refactoring / optimization.

0.8.0       2020-09-29
    - Extract and spin-off Parallel::ForkManager::Segmented::Base with
    process_args().

0.6.0       2020-07-30
    - Add DESCRIPTION and SEE ALso to the POD.
    - Use a better example in the SYNOPSIS.

0.4.0       2020-07-27
    - Add the stream_cb option.
    - Convert weaver.ini to @SHLOMIF

0.2.0       2019-09-10
    - Add process_batch .

0.0.2       2018-08-23
    - Fix a bug with calling the callback with undef() once on empty
    input.
    - Add tests.

0.0.1       2018-08-15
    - First version, released on an unsuspecting world
